mbassy of the Philippines \u2013 News |url=http://www.philippineembassy-usa.org/news/5547/300/BE-A-FILIPINO-AMBASSADOR-IN-YOUR-OWN-RIGHT-US-SOUTHEAST-COMMUNITIES-INVITED-TO-JOIN-11TH-AMBASSADORS-TOUR/d,phildet/ |accessdate=19 April 2019 |work=Embassy of the Philippines, Washington D.C. |date=7 April 2017 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190419060439/http://www.philippineembassy-usa.org/news/5547/300/BE-A-FILIPINO-AMBASSADOR-IN-YOUR-OWN-RIGHT-US-SOUTHEAST-COMMUNITIES-INVITED-TO-JOIN-11TH-AMBASSADORS-TOUR/d,phildet/ |archivedate=19 April 2019}}</ref>\n* ''\"Crown Jewel of Mindanao\"''<ref name=\"Inquirer-AtThePeak\">{{cite news |last1=Remo |first1=Amy R. |title=At the Peak of Davao City's great adventures |url=https://business.inquirer.net/268195/at-the-peak-of-davao-citys-great-adventures |accessdate=19 April 2019 |work=Philippine Daily Inquirer |date=6 April 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190408182651/https://business.inquirer.net/268195/at-the-peak-of-davao-citys-great-adventures |archivedate=8 April 2019 |language=en}}</ref>\n* ''\"Durian Capital of the Philippines\"''<ref name=\"SunStar-DurianCapital\">{{cite news |last1=Bautista |first1=Debb |title=Davao, Durian Capital of the Philippines |url=https://www.sunstar.com.ph/article/1779849 |accessdate=19 April 2019 |work=Sunstar |date=21 December 2018 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181221212828/https://www.sunstar.com.ph/article/1779849 |archivedate=21 December 2018 |language=English}}</ref>\n* ''\"Fruit Basket of the Philippines\"''<ref name=\"Inquirer-ChinaTradeFair\">{{cite news |last1=Mangosing |first1=Frances |title=Davao region 'charms' at China trade fair |url=https://business.inquirer.net/178969/davao-region-charms-at-china-trade-fair |accessdate=19 April 2019 |work=Philippine Daily Inquirer |date=18 September 2014 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016170322/http://business.inquirer.net/178969/davao-region-charms-at-china-trade-fair |archivedate=16 October 2015 